Hi Aditya,

Yes you are correct that Subread reports no more than 16 alignments per reads. One reason for this limitation is because subread detects indels in the read (Bowtie does not detect indels) and it has to set a limit on the number of candidate locations being considered due to the computational cost consideration.

Thanks for considering Subread and good luck for your project.

Wei

