Please be patient in this regard. The reviewer will get to your package as soon as they can. Each package takes time to review, and each reviewer is reviewing multiple packages. 

As far as asking for support regarding your package, it is best to ask your questions on the "Issue" which was created for the package contribution.  If you have general Bioconductor questions, the support site can help you as well, support.bioconductor.org. If you are unsure, bioc-devel mailing list is the right place. 

Best,

Nitesh 

